{"tid":1670011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[釐清概念]加泰集會與香港本土政治無關","createTime":"2019-10-23T00:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T01:24:58.000Z","uid":77393,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7078112fddd96b95ef094b8f01e252562c01dda2","tid":1670011,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T00:36:55.000Z","msg":"以大會澄清嘅目的 不論警暴 政治打壓可以同香港情況都有相似地方<br />\n<br />\n而家個集會僅僅係對加泰示威嘅一個支持<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但同香港政治絕無關係</span><br />\n<br />\n集會係有自由 當然可以繼續搞 亦都尊重同體諒搞手 而各種利弊好多post已經討論咗<br />\n<br />\n而大家要認清集會目的 同香港本土係冇關係 大家支持亦可以去參與 我哋爭取民主社會就要學識所有不同聲音<br />\n<br />\n所以最後建議文宣group將加泰集會剔出香港人日程表 因為集會內容同香港本土革命無關 為免手足誤會 大會要宣傳就分開搞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"e42993e6dbe87fd8da3f364654a00e5c30a1c65a","tid":1670011,"uid":268462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T00:37:33.000Z","msg":"[可唔可以大和解］加泰搞手 全香港人求下你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1669934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1669934</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"42ab8595f7ad562af1671a7da5ea8d3a95ec6c32","tid":1670011,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T00:39:37.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"2b15e9c32adc50c2532ee19c7d42144436794c20","tid":1670011,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T00:44:00.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"7a48de25d726a3809cd4844ebbb6f825b3a01568","tid":1670011,"uid":130079,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T00:44:27.000Z","msg":"出到國際人地點解讀就另一件事<br />\n<br />\n又要做死文宣組？"},{"pid":"dd05afc5a2693b5f4210788a17665a932b5d11bd","tid":1670011,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a48de25d726a3809cd4844ebbb6f825b3a01568","tid":1670011,"uid":130079,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T00:44:27.000Z","msg":"出到國際人地點解讀就另一件事<br />\n<br />\n又要做死文宣組？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T00:58:01.000Z","msg":"將佢剔出日程表我諗應該唔係要做好多嘢 另外佢自己集會嘅宣傳其實已經好多 至少連登已經好多熱門po"},{"pid":"93bbde7e767c013249de0f6561920681f7c612a4","tid":1670011,"uid":44309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T00:58:44.000Z","msg":"唔會去 Bye9Bye"},{"pid":"5180963b7424954f3ae8a50bcfe3c42fb5e6cc0e","tid":1670011,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabcf35b08ba50c6efde0579eefb60b9a5663e9a","tid":1670011,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:24:58.000Z","msg":"3/10"}]}